fig.basic
Class LogInfo

java.lang.Object
  fig.basic.LogInfo

public class LogInfo
extends Object

The logging output has a tree structure, where each node is a line of output, and the depth of a node is its indent level. A run is the sequence of children of some node. A subset of the lines in the run will get printed.
